node.text: Adventures at West Lake Trail Onondaga Park this morning.
Summer breezes on Mum and Pop’s porch.
Advice of spring at my mom and dads. 🙂
With everything gone, I’m remembering the reasons I fell in love with my home all those years ago.  On to the next chapter.
I think the eyebrows did it.
Stockings are hung... waiting for  Santa 🎅🎄🎁
